            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><div n="1" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Silvano <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>ro</ex></expan> <supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>alute</ex></expan></supplied> <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>C</abbr><ex>ai</ex></expan> Pomini <supplied reason="lost" cert="low">--</supplied> <lb n="3"/>Decsiani <note>sic</note> pr<gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> <lb n="4"/><expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>ionis</ex></expan> II <expan><abbr>ad</abbr><ex>iutricis</ex></expan> ex voto <lb n="5"/>equisiones eius </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> <expan><abbr>pos</abbr><ex>uerunt</ex></expan>
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Decsiani: offensichtlich Schreibfehler für gemeint Dexianus oder Deccianus. Nach Birley C. Pominius möglicherweise Schreibfehler des Steinmetzen für P. Cominius (vgl. TitAq). Textwiedergabe nach TitAq.</p>
            </div>
